data.description: Welcome home to this completely renovated split level home in Hickman! Enjoy those summer evenings on the huge deck and cozy up next to the fire-pit in the backyard. With plenty of room for a garden and a 10x12 shed with electricity and a two story garden shed, there’s no lack of outdoor storage. All of this surrounded by a wood privacy fence.  Inside, you will find a gorgeous kitchen with butcher block counters and a huge island, perfect for entertaining. The kitchen is part of an open floorplan with vaulted ceilings. On this main level, you will also find three bedrooms and one bathroom.  Head downstairs to see the newly finished primary suite, with brand new en suite bathroom and walk-in closet. You will also find the laundry room and the two stall garage downstairs. All of this can be found in a beautiful home at the end of a cul-de-sac. Schedule a tour today to see all the features to this truly amazing home!
